  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tricycle driver killed in Katunayake area",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 38-year-old tricycle driver was murdered in Katunayake, Mahagama Hinadiyana area last Sunday (17) night.",
        "The police said that the deceased was killed while he was going to a fuel filling station.",
        "The police mentioned that a group in another tricycle attacked with swords last night and carried out the murder.",
        "It is to be noted that the police have further stated that the murder took place due to a personal dispute and the suspects have not been identified yet."
      ],
